<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="minor-adj">minor <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'maɪnə(r)/    美 /'maɪnər/  </p>
<p>[常用于名词前，无比较级变化]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>较小 / 少的；轻微的；次要的</strong></h4>
<p>反 major </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>minor injury</strong> / <strong>illness</strong> 
轻伤/小病</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Luckily it was only a minor problem. 
幸运的是，那只是个小问题。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>（音乐）小调的；小音阶的</strong></h4></div>